                <note rend="inline" type="source">837.51/594: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Cuba</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Cable</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-09-28T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 28, 1921—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>158. For General Crowder.</p>
                <p>Your 119, September 25, noon.</p>
                <p>Dwight Morrow, partner of J. P. Morgan &amp; Company, accompanied by Norman
                    Davis, will leave Washington for Havana on September 29, to confer with you and
                    later with the Cuban Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
